	Let $k\ge 2$ and  $A\in \GL_2(\Z)$ has a real eigenvalue $\lambda>1$. 
 Then there exists a mutually cobounded $(\LL^\infty,\exp^\diamond)$-measure equivalence coupling from $\Lamp_k$ to $\SOL_A=\Z^2\rtimes_A\Z$.

